1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:07,000
This is Agent Board:
a local AI ops cockpit with built-in safety and observability.

2
00:00:07,000 --> 00:00:16,000
I can switch between Developer, Research, and Safe Chat,
each with server-enforced policies.

3
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:28,000
Sessions are persistent and tied to user context.
I'll start with a normal request.

4
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:39,000
Unsafe prompts are intercepted before model execution
and returned as controlled refusals.

5
00:00:39,000 --> 00:00:49,000
Those safety outcomes are measured in real time
in the metrics dashboard.

6
00:00:49,000 --> 00:00:57,000
OpenTelemetry traces make critical-path debugging
fast and transparent.

7
00:00:57,000 --> 00:01:00,000
Agent Board:
local-first AI operations you can trust.
